com.serena.dmclient.objects
Interface ReplicationConfiguration

All Superinterfaces:
DimensionsObject
All Known Subinterfaces:
BaselineReplicationConfiguration, ItemReplicationConfiguration, RequestReplicationConfiguration
public interface ReplicationConfiguration
extends DimensionsObject

Represents an abstract Dimensions replication configuration. Replication configurations are used to control the replication of Dimensions objects between base databases. Currently, two types of configurations that can be defined: baseline configurations and item configurations.
